snippet.title: Evercade Namco Collection 2 Cartridge Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit: http://evercade.co.uk/namco-collection-2-cartridge/

The Namco Collection 2 cartridge brings 11 more classic games to the Evercade, including: Pac-Attack, Galaga, Splatterhouse 2, Splatterhouse 3 and more! The cartridge will be supplied in a stunning collectable retro style physical case with full colour manual!

Full games list:

Galaga
Pac-Attack
Tower of Druaga
Phelios
Dragon Spirit
Dig Dug 2
Burning Force
Weapon Lord
Warp Man
Splatterhouse 2
Splatterhouse 3

BURNING FORCE™, DIG DUG™II, DRAGON SPIRIT™THE NEW LEGEND, GALAGA™, PAC-ATTACK™, PHELIOS™, SPLATTERHOUSE™ PART 2, SPLATTERHOUSE™ 3, THE TOWER OF DRUAGA™, WARP MAN™ &
©BANDAI NAMCO Entertainment Inc.
